How to run on Windows
=====================

Pre-requisites
--------------
- Python2.7 32-bit - http://www.python.org/download/releases/2.7.5/
- Steam API key - http://steamcommunity.com/dev/apikey
- Steam ID (64-bit ID) - How do I find this? See below
- Have downloaded replays in the DotA2 client

Steps
-----

1. Clone repo
2. Install 
3. Run bootstrap.bat to install remaining dependencies
4. Run augr.bat to start program


How do I find my 64-bit Steam ID?
---------------------------------

1. Find your vanity name from your profile URL: http://steamcommunity.com/id/<vanity_name>/
2. Query Steam API for your Steam ID: https://api.steampowered.com/ISteamUser/ResolveVanityURL/v0001/?key=<key>&vanityurl=<vanity_name>
